dct_description_sm: Map upper right indicates that the map number is "12" Includes location map. Map shows international, inter-territorial, provincial and district boundaries, principal roads and railways. "Published by the Directorate of Colonial Surveys D.C.S. 17/11"; "10,500/9/48 S.P.C."
